<TEXT>
an apologetic note was left in the car 
of a winery worker before he allegedly slit the throats of his 
three young daughters court documents revealed monday 
the fbi meanwhile joined the hunt for ramon salcido 28 who 
was charged with four counts of murder and three counts of 
