gasoline prices around the country rose 
suddenly after the exxon valdez spilled 10 million gallons of oil 
in alaska but exxon and a government energy official told a senate 
hearing the accident wasnt the reason 
that wasnt enough to convince sen howard metzenbaum dohio 
