the liberation of palestinegeneral command remain in 
investigative custody in west germany following their arrest in 
october after what police said was the biggest illegal weapons bust 
in the nations history 
prechtel said the bomb that exploded monday was discovered 
during investigation of the palestinians but he and other 
officials declined to say when or where the explosive device was 
found 
