featuring coleader jim mesich an environmental consultant on his 
euphonium a higherpitched cousin of newbergers plumbing mesich 
once adlibbed the vocal in lamenting verses for a deceased 
grandchild his wife had to leave the room jazz is communication 
of soul newberger once reduced a pub full of scots to tears 
