other casinos its four properties will be tropworld casino and 
entertainment resort in atlantic city tropicana resort and casino 
in las vegas ramada express hotel casino laughlin nev and 
eddies fabulous 50s casino in reno 
he said the new company would employ about 10000 people ramada 
currently employs about 20000 half in its gaming operations 
5600 in the hotel group and about 3400 in the restaurant 
business 
